<head>INTRODUCE</head>
    <list type="altnames">
<item>PRESENT (FORMALLY)</item>
<item>MAKE KNOWN</item>
<item>ACQUAINT WITH</item>
    </list>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">介紹</item>
        <item xml:lang="och">媒</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>SHOW HUMANS to each other so as to CAUSE them TO MUTUALLY ADDRESS each other AND to INTERACT.</p>
    <div type="definition" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-12T16:57:34.278+09:00">
            <p>SHOW HUMANS to each other so as to CAUSE them to INTERACT.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. Such common words as exist refer to introducing marriage candidates to each other, such as méi 媒 acting on behalf of males and shuò 妁 on behalf of females.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>介紹</p>
<p>紹介</p>
<p>先容</p>
<p>先游 refers to introducing someone by way of recommending him to someone.</p>
<p>引見</p>
<p>牽線</p>
<p>穿針引線</p>
<p>拉線搭橋</p>
<p>first rough draft to identify synonym group members for future analysis 18.11.2003. CH</p>
        </div>
